HELLO DECEMBERRRRR!!! 🎄❄️☃️🏂 straight up, i’m so excited for this month lol. we’re heading on a pretty epic trip with a brand next week which will also double as our puppymoon — as we like to call it lol. our little man comes home in TWO weeks and i don’t even know how to explain our level of excitement!!! 🥹💕anyways, enjoy this lil video of us decorating our apartment xo

september you were chaotic af lololol! between re-organizing / re-decorating quite literally our whole apartment, getting rid of my entire closets for my “rebrand” as i like to call it hahah, dealing with wests craziness after his neuter and trying to get to the bottom of this mysterious sickness that’s been popping up all year… ya girl is exhaustedddddd yet refuelled at the same time?!😂 everything finally feels like it’s coming together and our space is so cozy and COMFORTABLE which is a wonderful change since we’re home A LOT. little man is back to being his happy little self and a lottttttt more tolerable after getting his plums chopped (iykyk) HAHA! anywaysssss, I hope spoooooky season is a little extra good to you all this year, love you lots😘🎃🍂👻
